import React, { Component }  from 'react'

import '../../normalize.scss'
import '../../base.scss'

import Banner from '../../components/Header/Banner'
import SobreDescricao from '../../components/Sobre/SobreDescricao'
import SobreDesafios from '../../components/Sobre/SobreDesafios'
import SobreJogos from '../../components/Sobre/SobreJogos'
import View from "../view/view"
import logo from '../../components/Header/Banner/destaques/Home/destaque-home.png'

import imgBanner from '../../components/Header/Banner/destaques/Home/1280.png';

class Home extends Component {
  render() {
    let contentBanner = "A Vitória só depende de Você!"
    return (
      <View public={true}>
        <Banner imagemBanner={imgBanner} imagem={logo} text={contentBanner}/>
        <SobreDescricao/>
        <SobreDesafios/>
        <SobreJogos/>
      </View>
    )
  }
}

export default Home
